Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.18,0:00:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（时空幻境之永恒传奇  4）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要拯救世界的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.11,0:00:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱离走向毁灭的大崩落危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不断旅行的里德，法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.62,0:00:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.22,0:00:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停留的海上都市・贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满了许多的迷团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.06,0:00:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在地下的那些蒙面人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.86,0:00:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有等待里德他们的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.23,0:00:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又将会如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…故事已渐入佳境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（时空幻境之永恒传奇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第10话  消失在夕阳里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，治愈功没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是剑上有涂什么特殊的药吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是可莉娜怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身上并没有受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是一直昏迷不醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.13,0:02:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.13,0:02:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇上好像发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡纽的所有居民听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时刻终于到来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.85,0:03:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们跟随奈雷特神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说住在这岛上的居民…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是“奈雷特福音”的手下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也并非全部都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果其中也有来自大陆的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.73,0:03:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必也有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不顺从艾克丝西亚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且听说过去也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗艾克丝西亚的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之这岛上大部分的居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是赛雷斯提亚人的后裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后至今仍对茵费利亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀恨在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.41,0:03:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她们为什么要做那种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  接下来打算怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之得先夺回大晶灵才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是岛上的居民全都是敌人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之先找个地方躲起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以到这附近的无人岛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说要去无人岛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用游泳的过去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过可莉娜现在这个样子的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期盼吾神奈雷特荣耀满身…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  继续报告吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前岛民们的武装化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正一步步的进行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有岛上的茵费利亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也都全部逮捕起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且遣送到收容所去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些虽是我们的岛民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不赞同我们计划的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也同样送往那个地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基于大晶灵还处于不稳定状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在发动总攻击之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还需要再等一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此这段时间动员所有的人手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕里德・哈谢尔那帮人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是…不论死活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人乖乖的坐着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像没追上来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是躲在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想伺机抓我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮  玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮是我们的朋友耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没理由让她一个人去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.35,0:05:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.65,0:05:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给你了  咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.03,0:06:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通缉中的玛萝妮・布鲁卡诺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用急，我是来投降的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.61,0:06:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了  凭玛萝妮的身手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会被那些家伙抓到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用那个混进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我紧张的要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，有用有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，好像不太有用耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得玛萝妮她们走到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮我转告艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮・布鲁卡诺希望见我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  带她到塔斯帖克的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要对她太失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.81,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.84,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是非常抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前我们有来过这里对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚！  里特，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.29,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的脸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.87,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在什么时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现到我的真正身分？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我们第一次见面的那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…那时候并没有叫我呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.14,0:10:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法确认你真正的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然这也跟你父亲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯帖克・布鲁卡诺有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.72,0:10:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是无法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.95,0:10:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒的女儿…对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实你父亲在过去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们“奈雷特福音”里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一位优秀的干部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我们这些侥幸生还的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.93,0:10:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要长久生存是不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不得不承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.34,0:10:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟茵费利亚人交往的屈辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过对于我们这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道地的赛雷斯提亚人而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.51,0:10:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就需要制造血统上极接近的后代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是塔斯帖克他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却想出与茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共同生存的愚蠢想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后把“奈雷特福音”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,置于岛上不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带着茵费利亚人的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及两人所生的小孩离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.13,0:11:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错…学识渊博的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有温柔的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们三人开始在大陆旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝着妈妈的故乡前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到那天为止…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.11,0:11:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母亲都已经不在人世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.05,0:11:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于这座岛的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有“奈雷特福音”的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从小就有听父亲跟我提起过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲的确是有讲过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于茵费利亚的报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一种空洞的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法和我父亲并不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让我加入“奈雷特福音”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会相信你的话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你有你父亲的风采
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却远如是茵费利亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何况加上塔斯帖克的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更是不可能会相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你怀疑我的忠诚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么收拾里德・哈谢尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.10,0:12:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一行人的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.13,0:12:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就请交给我来负责吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会杀了他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并带回在他们手上的可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把可莉娜带回来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，那就不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我已经得到了大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.64,0:12:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要那女孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.18,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何况我是假装是那女孩的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她抚养长大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了得到大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来可莉娜被艾克丝西亚骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗她说她们两个人是母女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你利用亲子之间的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.20,0:13:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种冷酷…令我深深的臣服不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你会说出这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛…玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.78,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎可以信任呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮・布鲁卡诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的头抬起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你振作一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…妈妈呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回…回去贝鲁卡纽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.26,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.47,0:14:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这的确是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有这个艾拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能证明你是我们的同胞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，只有这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才证明我是我父亲的孩子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.19,0:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的仇我终于…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.01,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾，你没有替你父母报到仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没看出那是我的影子对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死你父母的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是幻影呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少装蒜了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些怪物是你派去的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为的是要封住我爸爸的口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作点，玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这倒替我省了不少时间去找你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大晶灵就在眼前的说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你闪开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.39,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要亲手杀了艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.86,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是机会  只有改天再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧！法拉  玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点，玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在战斗也只有白白送死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就豁出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.34,0:15:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.74,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么傻话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是这时候死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.81,0:15:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就正如艾克丝西亚的愿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真是一场闹剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁沙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是逃不出我的手掌心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.24,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底要不要紧啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前它受的伤还没完全治愈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  巴鲁沙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.21,0:16:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊，巴鲁沙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师，他们开始行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有办法从这边过去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没有办法  人手不够啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这个时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮  把速度降慢一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.28,0:17:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.49,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害你们两个干的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.47,0:17:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.97,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，干的好干的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁沙你看  大家都逃之夭夭耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.82,0:17:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧，里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁沙，你不要紧吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.72,0:18:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来也只有拼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑着点  巴鲁沙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉，里德就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.50,0:18:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧，里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.34,0:18:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉，等里德伤好了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我带句话给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说我很喜欢他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提  我也很喜欢你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成玛萝妮你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.33,0:18:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.03,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.26,0:18:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德，玛萝妮她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德  法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这条命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你们能继续活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.85,0:19:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像过去我爸爸为我做的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.89,0:19:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.96,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.09,0:19:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.79,0:20:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮  你回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好  玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是好朋友吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以我求你回来好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背负着悲伤过去的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.61,0:20:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了挚爱的友人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失在故乡贝鲁卡纽的上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.32,0:20:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待…下回精彩好戏
